      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;about&#34;&gt;About&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr. Gavin James Wood is an influential English computer scientist and entrepreneur who has fundamentally shaped modern blockchain architecture. As a co-founder of Ethereum, he contributed to the foundational concepts of smart contracts and the Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM). Subsequently, he founded Polkadot and Kusama, designing next-generation blockchain ecosystems focused on interoperability and scalability.&lt;/p&gt;
